{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062400/extras/library_logo_transparent.png?t=1730749868\" />Welcome to Terra Alia, an enchanting realm where technology, magic, and language seamlessly intertwine, bringing a unique take on discovering a new language and making it into an interactive, immersive experience. <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062400/extras/Title-Mystery.png?t=1730749868\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Embark on a journey guided by Professor Esperanto, delving into a world of secrets and puzzles as you search for the missing mentor in Terra Alia's magical academy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062400/extras/1-Embark_1.gif?t=1730749868\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062400/extras/Title-Learn-1.png?t=1730749868\" />Dive into English, Spanish, Italian, French, German, Russian, Japanese, Korean, Chinese, and Brazilian Portuguese. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062400/extras/2-Languages.gif?t=1730749868\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062400/extras/Title-Leveling.png?t=1730749868\" />Enhance your abilities by learning new words, unlocking magical items, conversing with other characters, and exploring the world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062400/extras/3-Learning.gif?t=1730749868\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062400/extras/Title-Quests-1.png?t=1730749868\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Unravel clues, complete quests, and discover the secret behind Esperanto's disappearance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062400/extras/4-Puzzle.gif?t=1730749868\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062400/extras/Title-Combat-1.png?t=1730749868\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience VR-crafted language-based combat, strategically adapting to diverse enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062400/extras/5-Combat.gif?t=1730749868\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062400/extras/Title-Multiplayer.png?t=1730749868\" />Gather up to four friends for intense 2vs2 matches at the Downtown level. Test linguistic prowess in three rounds, with matches available in ten languages! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062400/extras/7-Multiplayer.gif?t=1730749868\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062400/extras/Title-Buddies.png?t=1730749868\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Unleash your inner collector and gather these adorable wooden figures across the gaming realm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062400/extras/6-Buddy.gif?t=1730749868\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062400/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730749868","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062400/page.bg.jpg?t=17307498